import { Box,Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import "./Product.css"
import Rough from './Rough'
import { detailData } from '../../../services/redux/State'

function Product() {

  return (
    <Box style={{'display':'flex','justifyContent':'center'}}>
        <Box className='productDetail'>
        <Typography
            variant="p"
            component="p"
          >
           Apple Product
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            className='li'
            component="p"
            sx={{fontSize:"25px"}}
          >
           New Apple AirPods (3D Generation)
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            className='li'
            component="p"
          >
           It's magic, remasterd!
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            component="ul"
            sx={{margin:"10px 0 10px"}}
          >
          {detailData.map(elem=>{
            return (
              <Typography
              variant="p"
              component="li"
              className='li'
              sx={{margin:"10px 0 10px"}}
            >
              {elem}
            </Typography>
            )
          })}
          </Typography>
        </Box>

        <Box>
            <Rough/>
        </Box>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Product
